data.description: Fantastic investment opportunity in the thriving heart of Passyunk Square. This lovingly maintained duplex is perfect for an owner occupant or an investor. Currently both units are rented. The first floor is a 1 bedroom with high ceilings, a recently updated bath, outdoor space and laundry.  This unit is currently rented for $1400.00 a month and the lease ends 10/2024. The second apartment is a 2 bedroom, bi-level,unit with an updated kitchen and full size laundry room. This unit is currently rented for $2050.00 a month with the lease ending 11/2023. The building is an excellent opportunity for an owner occupant or just strictly an investment. Just steps away from the shopping and dining on Passyunk Ave, the Italian market, multiple grocery stores and the Broad Street Line. A short walk to Center city as well. The convenience of this location cannot be beat.
